Key Match Events: Grayson Allen scored 14 points in the final period
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Suns have won three of four since coach Mike Budenholzer reorganized the Suns' rotation with Bradley Beal coming off the bench
Lauri Markkanen led the Jazz with 24 points
Walker Kessler had 16 points and 13 rebounds for Utah, and former Sun Drew Eubanks also had 11 rebounds
Others: The Suns beat the Jazz for the third time this season
Mason Plumlee scored the first five Suns points (six for the game) and finished with 10 rebounds
Both play Sunday. Utah hosts Brooklyn and Phoenix hosts Charlotte
